cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.SE 

The paper discusses the challenges of controlling and analyzing the behavior of AI and AGI, which are core topics in the field of AI (cs.AI). The proposed approach involves modeling deleterious behaviors as psychological disorders, which requires an understanding of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and the ability to diagnose and treat such disorders, which involves robotics (cs.RO), control systems (cs.SY), and software engineering (cs.SE).
